articles.title: About this site
articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About me
I am Ajay Malik, an incoming senior at William Fremd High School. I like to ride my bike during the summer, and code in R and Python.
About the project
This project is titled “Distill Tutorial”, and I have created this project in order to learn how to make websites with Distill
Goals
To learn how to make neat websites using Distill
Titling is a bit weird but I will figure it out

To create easy-to-understand visualizations that are available on the web
“This is data science”
Preceptor

“Kane’s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp”

Distill is a publication format for scientific and technical writing, native to the web.
Learn more about using Distill for R Markdown at https://rstudio.github.io/distill.
